$ Oracle Option: Advanced Security
@ Advanced Security

Oracle Advanced Security provides the security features
  • *Transparent Data Encryption* (allows to encrypt some or all data stored in a database when exported using Data Pump or backed up with Recovery Manager)
  • → development/databases/Oracle/Options/advanced-security/Data-Redaction[Data Redaction] (allows redaction of sensitive → development/Data[data] that is returend to applications)

